               <code code="42232-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PRECAUTIONS SECTION"/>
               <title>Caution</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Folic Acid in doses above 1 mg may obscure pernicious anemia, in that hematological remission may occur while neurological manifestations remain progressive.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20120906"/>
            </section>
