               <title>
                  <content styleCode="emphasis">Additional Warning</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Accidental overdose of iron-containing products is a leading cause of fatal poisoning in children under 6. Keep this product out of the reach of children. In case of accidental overdose, call a doctor or poison control center immediately.</paragraph>
               </text>
